---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Hex Board" description="A Python hex board that draws a line between two selected hexes.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Hex Board</h1>
  </div>

  <p>A hex-based board built with Python. The pink line is automatically created between the red and blue hexes. Click either colored hex to reposition it.</p>

  <p><a href="https://github.com/jmfernandes/Python/blob/master/pyqt/hex.py" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View on GitHub &rarr;</a></p>

  <p>Large board:</p>
  <img src="/images/hex_big.png" alt="Large hex board" />

  <p>Small board:</p>
  <img src="/images/hex_small.png" alt="Small hex board" />
</BaseLayout>
